    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      330.93,
      493.45,
      361.42
    ],
    "text": "Two suspects wanted for a series of three-wheeler thefts arrested \u2013 Kiribathgoda Police",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.5600004196167
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      375.88,
      519.29,
      444.38
    ],
    "text": "On 31.03.2026, officers of the Kiribathgoda Police Station arrested a suspect in possession of crystal methamphetamine (\u201cice\u201d) and detained him under detention orders. Subsequent investigations revealed that the suspect was wanted in connection with four three-wheeler thefts reported to the Peliyagoda, Wattala, and Kelaniya Police Stations.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      458.94,
      521.38,
      527.42
    ],
    "text": "Based on information obtained from the suspect, indicating that the four stolen three-wheelers had been sold in the Hingurakgoda area, a team of officers conducted a raid on 06.04.2026 and apprehended a suspect on charges of purchasing and disposing of stolen property. Another individual who had prepared forged documentation was also arrested. All four stolen three-wheelers were recovered and taken into police custody.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      541.98,
      442.66,
      555.26
    ],
    "text": "The suspects are residents of the Hingurakgoda area, aged 61 and 75.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      569.73,
      450.1,
      583.01
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being conducted by the Kiribathgoda Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
